INFORMACOES-ADICIONAIS.DESCRICAO-INFORMACOES-ADICIONAIS:
The Memorial University Collective Agreement calls for evaluation of the file of a faculty member seeking tenure to be appraised by scholars satisfying the following conditions: 

1. be competent and recognized scholars external to the University in the relevant discipline; 
2. have a national or international reputation for excellence in their field; 
3. shall not currently be collaborating with a candidate nor have collaborated in the past five (5) years.
